v=c()
worddetect <- function(x){
  for (i in 1:length(x)){
    v = append(v,strsplit(x[i],"")[[1]][3])
  }
  v
}

a = worddetect(gf_combined$DBN)
gf_combined$Borough <- a

x <- str_extract(gf_combined$the_geom,"(?<=\\().*(?=\\))")
x <- unlist(strsplit(x," "))
odd <- seq(1,201,2)
even <- seq(2,202,2)
long <- c()
lat <- c()

for (i in 1:101){
  long[i] <- x[odd[i]]
  lat[i] <- x[even[i]]
}
gf_combined$long <- as.numeric(long)
gf_combined$lat <- as.numeric(lat)
